parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition cylinder can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, which can be a safety concern, especially if it happens in a hazardous location.
symptoms: The key has to be pushed hard or wiggled to start the engine
the engine hesitates to start
the engine won't start at all
the ignition switch pulls out when the key is removed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door locks and handles can cause the doors to not lock or unlock, which can be a safety concern, especially if it makes the vehicle more susceptible to theft or break-ins.
symptoms: The doors won't lock or unlock
the door handles are broken
the doors can't be opened or closed manually.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch can cause the door to open while driving, leading to accidents or injuries, or prevent occupants from exiting the vehicle in an emergency.
symptoms: Doors will not open from the outside
doors will not stay closed
doors will open while driving
difficulty opening or closing doors
broken door handles
rusting at the bottom of the door.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the subframe can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Vehicle stalls without warning
severe corrosion of the subframe.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle are not adequately protected.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
even when the vehicle is involved in a severe accident
resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard illuminates
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbag sensors can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in a crash, or the deployment of airbags in non-crash situations.
symptoms: Airbag sensors fail to detect the presence of a passenger
leading to the failure of airbags to deploy in a crash
or the deployment of airbags in non-crash situations.
